name: globeseekers yoga
description:
1.5 hours Ashtanga Vinyasa Yoga with modifications for all levels and fantastic view into nature. A good workout with a nice relaxing part to recharge your energy and let go.
Denise & Christian teach alternately and offer various yoga styles such as Ashtanga Vinyasa, Yin Yoga and Rocket Yoga, as well as Acro Yoga, Thai Yoga Massage, Yoga Philosophy & Health Coaching.
Place:Waldfestplatz Mayrhofen
Times:Wednesday 7.00 p.m. Saturday 10.00 a.m.
Depending on the interest and the current number of participants, further times and days are recorded. Please bring your own mat but Denise or Christian also always have some extra mats with them.
Costs:12 Euro for 1 x 1.5 hours & 10 Euro with block of ten
